      "id": "PopularPost143782",
      "post_content": "hm, majinara makes a good point, there ARE ways to use this card. but you have to have your deck built in a way where you can use it, it would probably work out pretty well in my black deck if it was black.\n  \n   \naaand besides that it's too likely to kill your creature to just pin it on your own creature willy nilly in hopes of buffing it, and it's too likely to buff a creature to put it on an opponents creature in hopes of killing it, there are better ways to kill a creature with a spell, and better ways to buff your own creature.",
      "posted_by": "supershawn",
